home.ME: Hello, I am Oğuzhan ÇART. Since my childhood, I have had a great fascination with technology and software. I have been trying to improve myself in the software field since middle school.I studied Informatics Department in Sultangazi Vocational High School. I am currently working as a Front-End Developer. I dedicate myself to continuous improvement and learning. If you have any questions or suggestions, do not hesitate to write.
